{
  "stem": "888.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had a little Torah, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He would run around with the Torah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was quite impressive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not a meeting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, you know, sometimes he would just go over and, you know, shake hands.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- I learned in his yeshiva, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I sometimes twice a week would attend, you know, his-- you know, like an examination.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You would stay in the line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you would go, and they would ask you a certain passage from the Talmud, or a certain passage from, from the, from the Bible, you know, and its commentaries, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then whatever he asked you, try to see how, how well you're doing, or you understand what-- you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was quite young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was only about 12, 12 and a half at that particularly time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you have a bar mitzvah?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was bar mitzvah in, in '43.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or the end-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wait a minute. 1929.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was eleven.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think I was bar mitzvah in 19-- or '42 or '43.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And times were already not the best.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, you know, the anti-Semitism was even in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, a kid could remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you couldn't walk on the street if you worked on, on, on you know, excluded places, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You also had to be afraid, you know, somebody shouldn't throw a stone at you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not so much the grown up people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the younger generation, you know, always used to be very, very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, you know, you look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you know, you were wearing payos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And even if you didn't, they-- for some reason or other, they recognize you.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
